{"tid":787480,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"［討論］來自新世界","createTime":"2018-08-20T16:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T16:50:43.000Z","uid":199414,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"bd51d28631959dc69a13f0c2c2e78767878c42c9","tid":787480,"uid":199414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T16:30:37.000Z","msg":"有無人有睇哩套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近睇左 會唔會太遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次想討論既係哩套野入面既「愧死機制」<br />\n<br />\n有睇既都知道 化鼠係無咒力既人類<br />\n之所以將佢地改造成化鼠係因為要將佢地喺愧死機制入邊剔除<br />\n而結局中亦都可以知道 即使知道左化鼠係同類 攻擊化鼠仍然係無觸發愧死機制<br />\n哩一點說明左改造為化鼠係非常之有效且無解<br />\n<br />\n劇中誘導我諗左好多<br />\n其中一樣係我發現愧死機制同同理心好似<br />\n相同地 我地對一啲極其醜陋既野都無乜同理心<br />\n例如曱甴 抆晒佢手手腳腳都唔會有任何內疚 甚至會有快感<br />\n但如果想像好似抆曱甴咁抆人啲手手腳腳 我地就會覺得心寒<br />\n如果日後科技真係發展到可以將人改造成另一種生物既樣<br />\n我諗道德真係會淪亡 亦都無人可以平等咁對待佢地<br />\n試諗下當你知道平時夜晚喺廚房見到嗰隻曱甴係你細佬<br />\n你可唔可以忍受佢同你食同一包薯片<br />\n我相信哩個case只有大愛撚先可以handle<br />\n所謂話 人性其實有好多bug 亦有好多弱點<br />\n究竟應唔應該去修正、點樣去修正<br />\n定係去防止bug發生？<br />\n<br />\n有錯請指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e070f6263b0ae59aa1bbfc3bbd9f7fab96939e","tid":787480,"uid":43516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T16:36:50.000Z","msg":"其實點解小真理亞望到自己手手腳腳個時都冇覺得自己係人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2ac31ba7575a2944f5af1b9f8d4580514f2b1e","tid":787480,"uid":199414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7e070f6263b0ae59aa1bbfc3bbd9f7fab96939e","tid":787480,"uid":43516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T16:36:50.000Z","msg":"其實點解小真理亞望到自己手手腳腳個時都冇覺得自己係人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T16:38:30.000Z","msg":"其實見過水都知自己係人啦<br />\n不過哩個唔係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c32b51d860e039e4b08bb017ee19620c6fbd03","tid":787480,"uid":199414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T16:39:41.000Z","msg":"有無人分享下自己既體會<br />\n或者答下我嗰三條問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ddd6f2ffbcdcc988ff83cd59653f66213a30ae","tid":787480,"uid":12569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T16:44:16.000Z","msg":"唔需要 因為俾人改到咁 佢哋一早已經唔係人類"},{"pid":"c05563a3314210ec847e35d716f88acd5869ce8b","tid":787480,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T16:48:48.000Z","msg":"呢個BUG係現實世界無乜大影響<br />\n係套野入面就話因為愧死所以解決唔到惡鬼姐"},{"pid":"a4b12f25faa5c67d90dc8f8817c3433c6ddaf323","tid":787480,"uid":199414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8ddd6f2ffbcdcc988ff83cd59653f66213a30ae","tid":787480,"uid":12569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T16:44:16.000Z","msg":"唔需要 因為俾人改到咁 佢哋一早已經唔係人類"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T16:50:14.000Z","msg":"佢地只係外表唔係人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁既話好易剝奪人哩個身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ac054dd90878d14bbc32f3a4795948cc613fa0","tid":787480,"uid":199414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c05563a3314210ec847e35d716f88acd5869ce8b","tid":787480,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T16:48:48.000Z","msg":"呢個BUG係現實世界無乜大影響<br />\n係套野入面就話因為愧死所以解決唔到惡鬼姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T16:53:30.000Z","msg":"I mean對醜陋既野無同理心<br />\n如果有科技可以令人天生樣衰到好似怪物<br />\n咁好易玩階級制度or掌控社會"},{"pid":"e6c02414073ce445cec18448ee480ff25d30b6c6","tid":787480,"uid":199414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T17:00:21.000Z","msg":"而家係太晏啲人瞓左定係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e03db1480dd9bc4513aaa540b5db1f9b30ef00b","tid":787480,"uid":199414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T17:06:35.000Z","msg":"其實我主要係想會愧死去探討人性、道德哩個範疇<br />\n科技發展得愈黎愈快<br />\n已經有啲觸碰到道德既灰色地帶<br />\n如果唔諗先一步<br />\n長久以來建立既道德體制將毀於一旦<br />\n無野可以介定道德與不道德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ff23cb34b034cd51bc8d2ad9a1eb1f7d8796bc","tid":787480,"uid":199414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T17:07:37.000Z","msg":"無人既話我瞓先<br />\n聽日仲要返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639d4009a2d958e04539a276edf6664d2119ea7f","tid":787480,"uid":91931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T17:13:51.000Z","msg":"順其自然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746f15116f89ff7cb0befb3ac67039e51b22dfa4","tid":787480,"uid":33473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T17:50:05.000Z","msg":"原作小說我覺得係上到神台的經典<br />\n動畫可取的係音樂人設<br />\n作畫A1崩少d地位會更高<br />\n雖然而加係我心目中都係最top果幾部"},{"pid":"75ace4fe4366d5a6b3320f1ed321a8e766be8166","tid":787480,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T18:25:33.000Z","msg":"唔駛計到咩人唔人類咁長遠，your face your fate"},{"pid":"75b777537c170e97ba9c59d4e5f5b90ff1b1fccd","tid":787480,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T18:46:38.000Z","msg":"冇咒力($力)就要注定做狗<br />\n<br />\n哭jor<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/024637_bc278b8fd8f19d52cdbd049b07c284e3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F024637_bc278b8fd8f19d52cdbd049b07c284e3.png&h=e8629b85&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c388460151a03a0a82eb966079ab7f406c77c5a","tid":787480,"uid":85084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T18:51:08.000Z","msg":"其實唔洗未來 你睇下黑人<br />\n雖然近代已經好好多 但都係仲有歧視<br />\n<br />\n而且我覺得唔係樣唔樣衰既問題 而係有無能力既問題<br />\n人類只會睇唔起比佢廢既野 （好似係"},{"pid":"461d764ad96665746eea84562d8ad47304ae349d","tid":787480,"uid":158820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20